\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 Deep Quaternion Networks (Chase Gaudet & Maida)\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0

\fs26 \cf0 Overview
\f1\b0 \uc0\u8232 Extends complex-valued networks further into quaternions (4D hyper-complex numbers), offering better convergence and accuracy in segmentation and classification with fewer parameters (e.g., KITTI segmentation performance improved IOU: real\u8239 =\u8239 0.747, complex\u8239 =\u8239 0.769, quaternion\u8239 =\u8239 0.827). ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/pdf/1712.04604?utm_source=chatgpt.com"}}{\fldrslt \ul arXiv}})\

