\f0\b\fs40 \cf0 1. Poincar\'e9 Embeddings (facebookresearch/poincare-embeddings)\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf0 Learn hyperbolic embeddings that represent hierarchical symbolic structures\'97like taxonomies\'97more efficiently than Euclidean embeddings, especially in low-dimensional settings ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/FractalNet%3A-Ultra-Deep-Neural-Networks-without-Larsson-Maire/d0156126edbfc524c8d108bdc0cf811cfe3129aa?utm_source=chatgpt.com"}}{\fldrslt \ul Semantic Scholar}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/abs/1705.08039?utm_source=chatgpt.com"}}{\fldrslt \ul arXiv}}).\

