\f0\b\fs40 \cf0 2. FractalNet\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf0 FractalNet deploys a macro-architecture based on recursive, self-similar \'93fractal\'94 blocks\'97no residual connections\'97but matches ResNet-level performance on CIFAR and ImageNet using 
\f0\b drop-path regularization
\f1\b0  ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/facebookresearch/poincare-embeddings?utm_source=chatgpt.com"}}{\fldrslt \ul GitHub}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://aclanthology.org/2021.insights-1.8.pdf?utm_source=chatgpt.com"}}{\fldrslt \ul ACL Anthology}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://rdrr.io/github/hwchang1201/poincare.embeddings/f/vignettes/poincare_embeddings.Rmd?utm_source=chatgpt.com"}}{\fldrslt \ul Rdrr.io}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/abs/1605.07648?utm_source=chatgpt.com"}}{\fldrslt \ul arXiv}}).\

