\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 What You\'92re Looking At: Shallow Neural Decision Forests\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf0 This repository implements 
\f0\b Shallow Neural Decision Forests (sNDFs)
\f1\b0 \'97a model introduced alongside Deep Neural Decision Forests (dNDFs) by Kontschieder et al. (ICCV 2015) ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://openaccess.thecvf.com/content_iccv_2015/papers/Kontschieder_Deep_Neural_Decision_ICCV_2015_paper.pdf?utm_source=chatgpt.com"}}{\fldrslt \ul CVF Open Access}}). In sNDF, decision trees (typically with no hidden layers) are embedded into a neural pipeline:\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls103\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 Uses 
\f0\b differentiable stochastic routing
\f1\b0  (soft decisions via sigmoid).\
\ls103\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 Joint or alternating optimization of split functions and leaf predictors.\
\ls103\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 Demonstrates strong performance on datasets like MNIST, UCI Adult, Letter, Yeast, and ImageNet, with shallow trees achieving competitive accuracy with far fewer parameters ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/chrischoy/fully-differentiable-deep-ndf-tf?utm_source=chatgpt.com"}}{\fldrslt \ul GitHub}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://openaccess.thecvf.com/content_iccv_2015/papers/Kontschieder_Deep_Neural_Decision_ICCV_2015_paper.pdf?utm_source=chatgpt.com"}}{\fldrslt \ul CVF Open Access}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/jingxil/Neural-Decision-Forests?utm_source=chatgpt.com"}}{\fldrslt \ul GitHub}}).\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\sa40\partightenfactor0

