\f0\b\fs40 \cf0 7) Final notes (gotchas we\'92ve already handled)\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls315\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Keep norm/activation consistent
\f1\b0  with pretrained; if you must change, reset BN stats and warm-start with a low LR warmup.\
\ls315\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 AMP + FSDP
\f1\b0 : use bf16 on Ampere+; prefer ShardedGradOp and our auto-wrap policy per family.\
\ls315\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 LoRA for conv
\f1\b0 : target 
\f0\b late blocks
\f1\b0 ; small rank (4\'968) usually sufficient; IA\'b3 gates are great when memory-crunched.\
\ls315\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 DropBlock vs Dropout
\f1\b0 : DropBlock for CNNs, dropout for heads; DropPath for ConvNeXt/ViT.\
\ls315\ilvl0
