\ls387\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 Vector outputs; squash nonlinearity: v_j = (||s_j||\'b2 / (1+||s_j||\'b2))(s_j/||s_j||).\
\ls387\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 Routing: c_ij = softmax(b_ij), s_j = \uc0\u931  c_ij \'fb_j|i.\
