\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 Mathematical Appendix (Part 5) \'97 Capsules & External Memory\
Capsule Networks (Dynamic Routing)\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls399\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Squash nonlinearity
\f1\b0 : v_j = (||s_j||^2 / (1 + ||s_j||^2)) * (s_j / ||s_j||), where s_j = \uc0\u931 _i c_ij ^u_ij and ^u_ij = W_ij u_i.\
\ls399\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Routing logits update
\f1\b0 : c_ij = softmax_j(b_ij); b_ij 
\f4 \uc0\u8592 
\f1  b_ij + ^u_ij \'b7 v_j.\
\ls399\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Dims
\f1\b0 : u_i 
\f6 \uc0\u8712 
\f1  R^\{d_in\}, v_j 
\f6 \uc0\u8712 
\f1  R^\{d_out\}, W_ij 
\f6 \uc0\u8712 
\f1  R^\{d_out\'d7d_in\}.\
\ls399\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Tune knobs
\f1\b0 : d_out (caps dim), routing iterations (1\'965), number of capsules per layer.\
\pard\pardeftab560\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 Neural Turing Machine (NTM) \'97 Read/Write\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls400\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Content addressing
\f1\b0 : w_c^t = softmax(\uc0\u946 ^t * cos(k^t, M^\{t\u8722 1\})), \u946 \u8805 0.\
\ls400\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Interpolation
\f1\b0 : w_g^t = g^t w_c^t + (1\uc0\u8722 g^t) w^\{t\u8722 1\}, g
\f6 \uc0\u8712 
\f1 [0,1].\
\ls400\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Shift
\f1\b0 : ~w^t = conv_shift(w_g^t, s^t) with shift distribution s.\
\ls400\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Sharpen
\f1\b0 : w^t 
\f6 \uc0\u8733 
\f1  (~w^t)^\{\uc0\u947 ^t\}, \u947 \u8805 1.\
\ls400\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Read
\f1\b0 : r^t = \uc0\u931 _i w^t_i M^\{t\u8722 1\}_i.\
\ls400\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Write
\f1\b0 : erase e^t 
\f6 \uc0\u8712 
\f1  [0,1]^W, add a^t 
\f6 \uc0\u8712 
\f1  R^W\uc0\u8232 M^t = M^\{t\u8722 1\} 
\f6 \uc0\u8857 
\f1  (1 \uc0\u8722  w^t e^\{tT\}) + w^t a^\{tT\}.\
\ls400\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Dims
\f1\b0 : memory M 
\f6 \uc0\u8712 
\f1  R^\{N\'d7W\}; weights w^t 
\f6 \uc0\u8712 
\f1  \uc0\u916 ^N.\
\ls400\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Tune knobs
\f1\b0 : N (slots), W (width), #read/#write heads, \uc0\u946 ,g,\u947  ranges.\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Dim ledger tips
\f1\b0 : Keep explicit N\'d7W memory sizes; ensure controller outputs (k^t,e^t,a^t,s^t) have correct shapes.\
\
\pard\pardeftab560\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 Mathematical Appendix (Part 6) \'97 PPO / GAE (RL)\
PPO Objective\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls401\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Probability ratio
\f1\b0 : r_t(\uc0\u952 ) = \u960 _\u952 (a_t|s_t) / \u960 _\{\u952 _old\}(a_t|s_t).\
\ls401\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Clipped surrogate
\f1\b0 : L^CLIP = E_t[ min( r_t A_t, clip(r_t, 1\uc0\u8722 \u949 , 1+\u949 ) A_t ) ].\
\ls401\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Value & entropy
\f1\b0 : L^V = (V_\uc0\u952  \u8722  V_targ)^2, L^H = \u8722 \u931  \u960 _\u952  log \u960 _\u952 .\
\ls401\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Total loss
\f1\b0 : L = L^CLIP \uc0\u8722  c1 L^V + c2 L^H.\
\pard\pardeftab560\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 GAE (Generalized Advantage Estimation)\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls402\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 \uc0\u948 _t = r_t + \u947  V(s_\{t+1\}) \u8722  V(s_t).\
\ls402\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 A_t = \uc0\u931 _\{l=0\}^\{T\u8722 t\u8722 1\} (\u947  \u955 )^l \u948 _\{t+l\}.\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Tune knobs
\f1\b0 : \uc0\u949  (clip), c1 (value coef), c2 (entropy coef), \u947 , \u955 , rollout length, minibatch size, learning rate.\

\f0\b Threading
\f1\b0 : Increase 
\f0\b\fs32 num_workers
\f1\b0\fs26  in RLlib for environment parallelism; constrain DataLoader workers to avoid contention on the same node.\
\
\pard\pardeftab560\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 Mathematical Appendix (Part 7) \'97 Advanced Blocks\
DNC (Differentiable Neural Computer)\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls403\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 Extends NTM with temporal linkage + usage vectors.\
\ls403\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Temporal linkage
\f1\b0 : L^t[i,j] tracks that memory i was written just before j.\
\ls403\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Precedence
\f1\b0 : p^t = (1\uc0\u8722 \u931  w_write^t) p^\{t\u8722 1\} + w_write^t.\
\ls403\ilvl0
