\ls417\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 BatchNorm: y = (x\uc0\u8722 mu)/sqrt(var+eps) * gamma + beta; running stats momentum m.\
