\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 3) Configuration Schema (host-injected)\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf0 metrics:\
  flops_backend: fvcore         # fvcore | thop | none\
  log_activations: false\
\
export:\
  onnx:\
    enabled: true\
    path: artifacts/model.onnx\
    opset: 17\
    dynamic_axes:\
      input: \{0: batch, 2: H, 3: W\}\
      output: \{0: batch\}\
    simplify: true\
    runtime_check: true\
    providers: [CPUExecutionProvider]  # or CUDAExecutionProvider\
\
precision: \{weights: bf16, activations: bf16, norm: fp32\}\
quant: \{base_bits: 4, adapters_bits: 16\}\
\
# NEW: Throttling & Scheduling\
throttle:\
  endpoints:\
    tune.submit: \{rps: 2, burst: 4, concurrent: 2\}\
    train.submit: \{rps: 4, burst: 8, concurrent: 4\}\
  resources:\
    cpu_cores: \{max_total: 32, max_per_job: 8\}\
    gpu_devices: \{max_total: 4, max_per_job: 1\}\
    mem_bytes: \{max_total: 128Gi, max_per_job: 16Gi\}\
    io_mb_s: \{max_total: 500, max_per_job: 150\}\
    net_mb_s: \{max_total: 1000, max_per_job: 300\}\
  hyperparams:\
    lr: \{rate_limit: per_minute: 100\}            # prevent floods of tiny LR scans\
    batch_size: \{min: 4, max: 1024, step: 4\}\
    img.size: \{allowed: [512,640,800,1024]\}\
\
scheduler:\
  job:\
    max_concurrent: 4\
    queue_capacity: 64\
    priority_classes:\
      - \{name: emergency, weight: 100\}\
      - \{name: high, weight: 10\}\
      - \{name: normal, weight: 1\}\
    fairness: drf                            # weighted fair share | DRF | strict-priority\
  trial:\
    algorithm: asha                          # asha | pbt | hyperband | random\
    asha: \{grace_epochs: 2, reduction_factor: 3\}\
    budget:\
      walltime_minutes: 240\
      gpu_hours: 20\
      flops_max: 2.0e15\
      params_max: 1.0e8\
  resource_placement:\
    pack: true                               # prefer bin-packing vs spread\
    affinities: \{require_gpu: true\}\
    topology:\
      numa_aware: true\
      node_labels: \{accelerator: nvidia\}\
\
\pard\pardeftab560\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 4) Throttling (Admission & Flow Control)\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls447\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Endpoint rate-limits
\f1\b0 : token-bucket (RPS/burst) per endpoint+tenant; reject or queue beyond limits.\
\ls447\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Concurrency gates
\f1\b0 : cap in-flight jobs/trials; backpressure to clients with 429 and Retry-After.\
\ls447\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Resource quotas
\f1\b0 : enforce max CPU/GPU/mem/IO/network per job and global totals; map to cgroups (local) or K8s requests/limits (cluster).\
\ls447\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Hyperparam guards
\f1\b0 : validate grid values (min/max/allowed sets, step) and change rates (e.g., lr sweep density), refuse pathological sweeps.\
\ls447\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Fairness
\f1\b0 : WFQ/DRF across tenants; priority classes with preemption.\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Admission Controller
\f1\b0  (pseudocode)\
def admit(job):\
    check_endpoint_rate(job.user, job.endpoint)\
    check_concurrency(job.user)\
    enforce_quotas(job.resources)\
    validate_grid(job.grid, policy.hyperparams)\
    enqueue(job, priority=job.priority)\
\
\pard\pardeftab560\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 5) Scheduling (Job / Trial / Resource)\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls448\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Job-level
\f1\b0 : priority queue; DRF (Dominant Resource Fairness) sharing across CPU/GPU/mem.\
\ls448\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Trial-level
\f1\b0 : ASHA/Hyperband early-stop poor configs; optional PBT (mutate/promote).\
\ls448\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Resource-level
\f1\b0 : Ray PlacementGroups with accelerators; GPU MIG partitions if available; NUMA pinning; disk/IO shaping.\
\ls448\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Budgets
\f1\b0 : per-study budget (wall-clock, GPU-hours, FLOPs, params); terminate/exclude out-of-budget trials.\
\ls448\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Preemption & checkpointing
\f1\b0 : periodic AIR checkpoints; resume on available nodes.\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 ASHA + DRF schedule loop
\f1\b0 \
while queue:\
  job = pick_by_priority_drf(queue)\
  if resources_available(job):\
      start_trials(job, algo=ASHA(job.conf))\
  else:\
      evict_or_wait()\
\
\pard\pardeftab560\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 6) Inference Scheduling & Throttling\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls449\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Dynamic batching
\f1\b0 : per-endpoint batch window (e.g., 5ms) + max batch size.\
\ls449\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Micro-batching
\f1\b0 : split large batches across streams; control GPU streams.\
\ls449\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 Rate-limit
\f1\b0 : tenant/endpoint RPS; queue depth; SLO timeouts.\
\ls449\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs26 ONNX providers
\f1\b0 : schedule across CPU/CUDA/MIG; fallbacks if EP unsupported.\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0

