\f0\b\fs40 \cf0 Mentor\'92s Guide (Part 3) \'97 Living Deep Learning Framework for Rewiring (TritRPC-first)\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf0 This guide ties together taxonomy, ontology, and implementation into a single 
\f0\b learning + mentoring framework
\f1\b0 . It teaches how to onboard, decompose, rewire, and mentor new models in the Atlas/OS Service ecosystem. It builds on the conceptual base (self\uc0\u8209 organization, reflexive hypergraphs, semantic fibration) and the operational base (Atlas/OS repo, Serve plane, Studies, and Grafana dashboard).\
